platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 驚きに満ちた冒険が待つ世界へ
駕馭元素之力 遨遊提瓦特大陸

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Elemental magic rules the land of Teyvat in the remarkable Genshin Impact—and as a powerful Traveler, you put this power to good use. Vibrant visual effects transform elemental blasts of fire, ice, and lightning into jaw-dropping spectacles. But it’s not just a looker: Genshin Impact’s beautiful open world is filled with thrilling quests and fascinating secrets. Climb mountains, cook meals, and soar through the skies as you search for your lost sibling—or simply get lost in Teyvat and see what happens.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Explore a new land, and meet amazing new characters.
